OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA wet start to the morning,
OL,6,Fwith rain clearing northwards. Soon
OL,7,Fbrightening up with a mixture of
OL,8,Fsunshine and showers, some heavy with
OL,9,Fthe risk of thunder. Windy at times,
OL,10,Fwith gales along the south coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FHeavy showers will clear
OL,13,Feastwards during the evening. Mostly
OL,14,Fdry overnight, with clear spells.
OL,15,FHowever, a few light showers remain
OL,16,Fpossible. Staying breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
